Package: PSPcleanTools
Type: Package
Title: Support for Cleaning and Curating Permanent Sample Plot Records
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Parvin", "Kalantari", , "parvin.kalantari@nrcan.rncan.gc.ca", 
          role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of this package is to support the cleaning, standardization,
             and quality control of Permanent Sample Plot (PSP) data. Specifically,  
             1- process_dbh_issues identifies and flags abnormal DBH values, 2- treenum_to_multiplePSP 
             detects and corrects inconsistencies where the same tree number is linked to multiple PSPs, 
             and 3- classify_tree_status uses tree measurement histories to classify individuals as Alive, 
             Mortality, or Regeneration. These tools are designed to be reusable across datasets, improving
             the reliability of PSP-based analyses.
